response.original_title: Masayang Kabukiran: An Intimate Serenade of Beautiful, Haunting, Traditional Filipino Music
response.overview: Presented by the CCP in cooperation with the Tribung Pilipino Cultural Foundation, this concert features soprano Rachelle Gerodias, baritone Byeong In Park, soprano Jasmin Salvo, tenor Arman Ferrer, and the Kabataang Gitarista, who will serenade you with a collection of well-loved kundiman, love songs, and many more.
response.title: Masayang Kabukiran: An Intimate Serenade of Beautiful, Haunting, Traditional Filipino Music
